## 動的テキストタグ [#ub9665f5]

### DefineEditText [#DefineEditText]

|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Header|RECORDHEADER|タグタイプ = 37.|
|CharacterID|UI16|ID for this dynamic text&br;character.|
|Bounds|RECT|Rectangle that completely&br;encloses the text field.|
|HasText|UB[1]|0 = text field has no default text.&br;1 = text field initially displays the&br;string specified by InitialText|
|WordWrap|UB[1]|0 = text will not wrap and will&br;scroll sideways&br;1 = text will wrap automatically&br;when the end of line is reached.|
|Multiline|UB[1]|0 = text field is one line only.&br;1 = text field is multi-line and&br;scrollable.|
|Password|UB[1]|0 = characters are displayed as&br;typed.&br;1 = all characters are displayed&br;as an asterisk.|
|ReadOnly|UB[1]|0 = text editing is enabled.&br;1 = text editing is disabled.|
|HasTextColor|UB[1]|0 = use default color.&br;1 = use specified color&br;(TextColor).|
|HasMaxLength|UB[1]|0 = length of text is unlimited.&br;1 = maximum length of string is&br;specified by MaxLength.|
|HasFont|UB[1]|0 = use default font.&br;1 = use specified font (FontID)&br;and height (FontHeight). (Can’t&br;be true if HasFontClass is true).|
|HasFontClass|UB[1]|0 = no fontClass, 1 = fontClass&br;and Height specified for this&br;text. (can't be true if HasFont is&br;true). Supported in Flash Player&br;9.0.45.0 and later.|
|AutoSize|UB[1]|0 = fixed size.&br;1 = sizes to content (SWF 6 or&br;later only).|
|HasLayout|UB[1]|Layout information provided.|
|NoSelect|UB[1]|Enables or disables interactive&br;text selection.|
|Border|UB[1]|Causes a border to be drawn&br;around the text field.|
|WasStatic|UB[1]|0 = Authored as dynamic text&br;1 = Authored as static text|
|HTML|UB[1]|0 = plaintext content.&br;1 = HTML content (see&br;following).|
|UseOutlines|UB[1]|0 = use device font.&br;1 = use glyph font.|
|FontID|If HasFont, UI16|ID of font to use.|
|FontClass|If HasFontClass, STRING|Class name of font to be loaded&br;from another SWF and used for&br;this text.|
|FontHeight|If HasFont, UI16|Height of font in twips.|
|TextColor|If HasTextColor, RGBA|Color of text.|
|MaxLength|If HasMaxLength, UI16|Text is restricted to this length.|
|Align|If HasLayout, UI8|0 = Left&br;1 = Right&br;2 = Center&br;3 = Justify|
|LeftMargin|If HasLayout, UI16|Left margin in twips.|
|RightMargin|If HasLayout, UI16|Right margin in twips.|
|Indent|If HasLayout, UI16|Indent in twips.|
|Leading|If HasLayout, SI16|Leading in twips (vertical&br;distance between bottom of&br;descender of one line and top of&br;ascender of the next).|
|VariableName|STRING|Name of the variable where the&br;contents of the text field are&br;stored. May be qualified with&br;dot syntax or slash syntax for&br;non-global variables.|
|InitialText|If HasText STRING|Text that is initially displayed.|


### CSMTextSettings [#CSMTextSettings]

|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Header|RECORDHEADER|タグタイプ = 74.|
|TextID|UI16|ID for the DefineText,&br;DefineText2, or&br;DefineEditText to which this&br;tag applies.|
|UseFlashType|UB[2]|0 = use normal renderer.&br;1 = use advanced text&br;rendering engine.|
|GridFit|UB[3]|0 = Do not use grid fitting.&br;AlignmentZones and LCD&br;sub-pixel information will not&br;be used.&br;1 = Pixel grid fit. Only&br;supported for left-aligned&br;dynamic text. This setting&br;provides the ultimate in&br;advanced anti-aliased text&br;readability, with crisp letters&br;aligned to pixels.&br;2 = Sub-pixel grid fit. Align&br;letters to the 1/3 pixel used&br;by LCD monitors. Can also&br;improve quality for CRT&br;output.|
|Reserved|UB[3]|Must be 0.|
|Thickness|F32|The thickness attribute for&br;the associated text field. Set&br;to 0.0 to use the default&br;(anti-aliasing table) value.|
|Sharpness|F32|The sharpness attribute for&br;the associated text field. Set&br;to 0.0 to use the default&br;(anti-aliasing table) value.|
|Reserved|UI8|Must be 0.|

### DefineFont4 [#DefineFont4]

|フィールド|型|コメント|
| --- | --- | --- |
|Header|RECORDHEADER|タグタイプ = 91|
|FontID|UI16|ID for this font character.|
|FontFlagsReserved|UB[5]|Reserved bit fields.|
|FontFlagsHasFontData|UB[1]|Font is embedded. Font tag includes&br;SFNT font data block.|
|FontFlagsItalic|UB[1]|Italic font|
|FontFlagsBold|UB[1]|Bold font|
|FontName|STRING|Name of the font.|
|FontData|FONTDATA[0 or 1]|When present, this is an OpenType&br;CFF font, as defined in the OpenType&br;specification at www.microsoft.com/&br;typography/otspec. The following&br;tables must be present: ‘CFF ’, ‘cmap’,&br;‘head’, ‘maxp’, ‘OS/2’, ‘post’, and&br;either (a) ‘hhea’ and ‘hmtx’, or (b)&br;‘vhea’, ‘vmtx’, and ‘VORG’. The ‘cmap’&br;table must include one of the following&br;kinds of Unicode ‘cmap’ subtables: (0,&br;4), (0, 3), (3, 10), (3, 1), or (3, 0)&br;[notation: (platform ID, platformspecific&br;encoding ID)]. Tables such as&br;‘GSUB’, ‘GPOS’, ‘GDEF’, and ‘BASE’&br;may also be present.&br;Only present for embedded fonts.|
